title: LEGENDS OF THE DARK KNIGHT 069 (2013) (Digital) (Darkness-Empire
description:
Legends of the Dark Knight #69

"The Echo of Pearls" part 1 of 1

When young Bruce Wayne accidentally discovered a cave on his family's estate, he was thrilled. All the best heroes have caves. But he wasn't alone that day -- and the echoes of his discovery reverberate throughout his life.

Written by Jim Krueger
Art by Tom Raney
Colored by Wendy Broome
Lettered by Saida Temofonte

Genres: Action/Adventure, Crime, Mystery, Superhero

23 Pages
Digital Release Date: Sep 26th 2013
Age Rating: 12+ Only
